Class AVLTree

  • java.lang.Object
    • AVLTree

  • public class AVLTree
extends java.lang.Object
    I'm using using this code from Assignment 3 to count the duplicates This is the AVL Tree Class Methods to Traverse through the tree by inOrder recursively displaying the values. The AVL tree class has deletion and insertion with is AVL compliance by checking the height of the right and left side
    Version:
    1.0 (October 2014) Compiler Version Java 1.7
    Author:
    Long Nguyen
